          standfirst:
            '<p>UK Ministry of Defence says poorly trained and equipped reservists struggling on the ground in Ukraine</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2022/nov/25/russia-ukraine-war-at-a-glance-what-we-know-on-day-275-of-the-invasion">What we know on day 275 of the invasion</a></li></ul>',
